data.description: Don't miss your chance for single story living in desirable Colony Pines! Freshly painted interior and so many updates! New granite counters in bathrooms and kitchen and all appliances replaced in 2020. LVP flooring and carpets were replaced in 2022. Bathrooms were retiled and new toilets installed in 2022. Custom wood blinds on bay window in kitchen installed in 2023. Roof replaced in 2019, HVAC and water heater replaced in 2020. Fully fenced backyard with a freshly stained deck.
